l review is below, but check out our current top 10 about <a href=\"/best-baby-video-monitors\">Baby Video Monitors</a>Â here.</em>","The Lorex Star Bright is a decent baby video monitor that will help put your mind at ease. The main appeal of baby video monitors is that they help you keep an eye on your infant while you&#39;re not in the same room. The Star Bright has all of the tools and features you need to do so, but it doesn&#39;t have quite as many features as some of the competition. While it isn&#39;t perfect, the Star Bright still gives you an extra set of eyes to keep track of your baby.","One of the most disappointing aspects of the Star Bright is its limited range. Lorex claims a range of up to 450 feet in ideal conditions. That number is based on an open-range test, meaning outdoors with no obstructions. The real range inside a home is going to be significantly less than that. This makes the Star Bright one of the worst performers in range on our lineup.","Perhaps the most obvious and attractive part of the Star Bright is its 7-inch screen. Many baby video monitors are stuck on tiny 2-inch screens. Some go up to 3.5 inches, but the Star Bright blows them all out of the water. This is the largest screen out of all of devices we looked at for our baby video monitor reviews. If a large screen is what you&#39;re after, then the Star Bright&#39;s shortcomings seem inconsequential.","You can use the Star Bright to communicate with your baby, even when you&#39;re in another room. This is similar to how walkie-talkies work, and it allows you to soothe your baby without being right there. The Star Bright also has VOX functionality, which wakes the device up when it hears noise in the baby&#39;s room. This serves to save battery life and grab your attention when the video feed starts up."]},"id":"5a9bae3d-9115-46b8-a1fa-46ce4c7c4826","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"b3077a03-baa4-42aa-9318-08046d9c5549","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Lorex Star Bright isn&#39;t the best baby video monitor on the market, but it does have some of the features and functionality you&#39;ll find on the best. The extra-large screen is very nice compared to the much smaller screens on most other monitors. However, the Star Bright&#39;s poor range can be problematic, especially if you have a large home, or there are many walls in your home. It&#39;s not perfect, but the Star Bright can give you greater peace of mind by keeping you constantly informed about your baby&#39;s status."]},"id":"a812a6c0-8241-42f0-b8d1-ec858f93c20f","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_64538","url":"/lorex-star-bright-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"john-carlsen","url":"/author/john-carlsen","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"John Carlsen","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"jN6fuw55cS2xYQi25mfgkg","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2015-04-29T19:48:44Z","datePublished":"2015-04-29T19:48:44Z","name":"Lorex Star Bright","synopsis":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about Baby Video Monitors here.","review":{"rating":86,"verdict":"Despite some flaws, like poor range, the Lorex Star Bright is a decent baby video monitor.","pros":["This monitor has a 7-inch screen, which is much larger than most other monitors."],"cons":["We weren&#039;t impressed with the device&#039;s range."]},"strapline":"Editor's Note: This review has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it no longer ranks as a top 10 product. The original review is below, but check out our current top 10 about Baby Video Monitors here.","language":"en","dateModified":"2015-04-29T19:48:44Z","id":"CnqXCtnyXX8Pke3WUKyHgM","meta":{"title":"Lorex Star Bright Review | Top Ten Reviews","description":"The Lorex Star B